---
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>About — Maker’s Note & Partnership</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Official Mythic GME 2e apps by Jason Holt Digital in partnership with Word Mill Creative." />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/global.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/7.0.0/css/all.min.css" />
    <link rel="canonical" href="https://jasonholtdigital.com/about/" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <a class="skip" href="#main">Skip to main content</a>
    <div id="bg-atmo" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div id="site">
      <Header />
      <main id="main" class="container" style="min-height:40vh; padding: 3rem 0;">
        <h1>About — Maker’s Note &amp; Partnership</h1>

        <section class="panel" aria-labelledby="makers-title" style="margin-top:1rem">
          <h2 id="makers-title">Maker’s Note</h2>
          <p>
            Hi, I’m Jason—an indie developer focused on tools that respect and amplify tabletop creativity. I build the
            <strong>official Mythic GME&nbsp;2e apps</strong> in partnership with Word Mill Creative, and I ship small, steady improvements
            because craft matters. When players tell me a feature cut friction from their session, that’s the win. If that sounds like your
            kind of software, welcome.
          </p>
          <p class="row" style="margin-top:.5rem">
            <a class="cta-brick" href="/blog">Read the Blog&nbsp;→</a>
            <a class="cta-brick" href="https://github.com/kingdomseed" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i class="fa-brands fa-github" aria-hidden="true"></i> View GitHub</a>
            <a class="cta-brick" href="https://discord.gg/PEDHrhzcnk" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i class="fa-brands fa-discord" aria-hidden="true"></i> Join Discord</a>
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="panel" aria-labelledby="wmc-title" style="margin-top:1rem">
          <h2 id="wmc-title">Word Mill Creative Partnership</h2>
          <p><strong>Official Licensee.</strong> Jason Holt Digital builds the licensed digital companions for Mythic GME&nbsp;2e. Our focus is player‑first, faithful to the system, and respectful of the text.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Official Mythic content implemented (Fate Chart/Check, Meaning tables).</li>
            <li>Cross‑platform releases (mobile + desktop).</li>
            <li>Community‑driven improvements.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="panel" aria-labelledby="timeline-title" style="margin-top:1rem">
          <h2 id="timeline-title">Short Timeline</h2>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>2024 →</strong> Full‑time indie; early Mythic prototypes.</li>
            <li><strong>2025 →</strong> Mobile + Desktop launched; community passes 200 members; 50k+ installs.</li>
            <li><strong>Next →</strong> Steady improvements, more resources, and broader distribution.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="panel" aria-labelledby="creds-title" style="margin-top:1rem">
          <h2 id="creds-title">Light Creds</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Flutter for iOS, Android, macOS, Windows, Linux</li>
            <li>Clean architecture, strong testing, simple UX</li>
            <li>Former CS educator; clear docs and examples</li>
          </ul>
          <p style="color: var(--muted)"><small>Employer/portfolio content stays here (About) and in Blog case notes. Keep the homepage player‑first.</small></p>
        </section>
      </main>
      <Footer />
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
